title: Tesla accused of firing union supporters days after organizing effort starts
description: Tesla has fired more than 30 supporters of a nascent union at its Buffalo facility, just days after the organizing effort was announced, according to the union.

title: SEC charges Terra founder Do Kwon with fraud
description: The US Securities and Exchange Commission has charged crypto developer Do Kwon and his company Terraform Labs with defrauding investors in what the regulator deemed a multibillion-dollar scheme, according to a filing in federal court.
